name: Com que parte do corpo pensa?
description: Digital collage with nonlinear glyph which means "what part of the body do you think?" in portuguese. (2480x3508px) Nonlinear glyph is a study I have been doing for 3 years about creating glyphs on a modular basis. you can find more information on instagram.com/valentim.ttt // Mateus Valentim, Designer and tattoo artist based in CWB/BR // twitter @vadevagarin
